        "heading": "Shedding more lately? There is usually a reason.",
        "body": "<p>Hair is one of the first places your body shows it is running low. Stress, busy seasons, restrictive eating, and everyday nutrient gaps can all push more strands out of their growth phase and into shedding.</p><p>The frustrating part: by the time you notice it in the brush or the shower drain, the gap has usually been building for weeks.</p><p>That is why topical products alone often disappoint. They work on the strand you already have. They cannot reach the follicle doing the growing.</p>",
        "closing_line": "Bloomli works from the inside, where the growth cycle actually starts.*",
        "use_custom_emphasis_color": true,
        "emphasis_color": "#7b2151",
        "heading_size": 46,
        "heading_size_mobile": 34,
        "padding_top": 96,
        "padding_bottom": 96,
